a9725aeff3f9c3135f8794d5ec617050421b7a0","tid":51574,"uid":5001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 鬧快寫字<br />\n多角度思考多條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本就限制住你諗咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最少佢令到學生會關心時事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然考嗰好好撚多野寫同埋ies好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果份卷cut一半題目就會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bde944a0f2e51eb6a9d54601df140c59fe80f9a","tid":51574,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文<br />\n教d野冇用<br />\n<br />\n淨係記得押韻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者<br />\n我是一名lihkg會員<br />\n我覺得強迫學生使用所謂書面語很戇鳩<br />\n因為現實中上班時根本沒有人會使用中文<br />\n此致<br />\nlihkg各會員<br />\n香港一百七十六年十二月廿三日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dd93746ec7d67115ca3032058c0fba55f14f92","tid":51574,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"中學時期最憎通識，亦都係通識最低分，但依家覺得通識最有用，而中文先係終極垃圾"},{"pid":"5587c07931438ba3686286f8aee5bd855be3ad24","tid":51574,"uid":21526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:45:14.000Z","msg":"最撚憎中文"},{"pid":"18476902a358adaba10f1ee7204645fbd60a434b","tid":51574,"uid":46513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"中英都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea90d2c2b015bce47a1d6cc6e7000ce6154c88e","tid":51574,"uid":13317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"中文"},{"pid":"8af58edcb5e7a1b38b0517ef3d05c90508a20ada","tid":51574,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s